OL,3,CBangkok fire death toll rises to 32 as
OL,4,Ctwo die in hospital
OL,6,FTwo more people have died after a fire
OL,7,Ftore through a bar in the Thai
OL,8,Fcapital, Bangkok, on Sunday, taking
OL,9,Fthe death toll to 32.
OL,11,FMore than 70 people were injured, with
OL,12,F15 still in intensive care, after the
OL,13,Fblaze at the Rong Beer Na Ladprao
OL,14,Fmusic bar.
OL,16,FThis is the city's deadliest fire
OL,17,Fsince 2009, when 66 people were killed
OL,18,Fin a blaze during a New Year's Eve
OL,19,Fcelebration at the Santika nightclub.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
