OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784135918
OL,3,CBangkok fire death toll rises to 32 as
OL,4,Ctwo die in hospital
OL,6,FThe cause of the fire is still under
OL,7,Finvestigation, with efforts
OL,8,Fconcentrated on ceiling materials and
OL,9,Fwhether emergency exits were blocked.
OL,11,FPolice said the majority of those
OL,12,Fkilled were found trapped in
OL,13,Fwindowless bathrooms, where they may
OL,14,Fhave been trying to escape the blaze.
OL,16,FMost died from smoke inhalation, and
OL,17,Fsome died from burn injuries, Wiroon
OL,18,FSupasingsiripreecha, chief of the
OL,19,FInstitute of Forensic Medicine, said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
