OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784135918
OL,3,CBangkok fire death toll rises to 32 as
OL,4,Ctwo die in hospital
OL,6,FNatthaphong Lakhorn, who was there on
OL,7,Fthe night and lost a relative in the
OL,8,Ffire, recalled seeing white smoke
OL,9,Fcoming from the stage.
OL,11,F"When the fire broke, I just ran, and
OL,12,Fthen all power went out," he said, "it
OL,13,Fwas so hectic."
OL,15,FNatthaphong escaped through the back
OL,16,Fdoor near the bathrooms, where a
OL,17,Fsecurity guard used a torch to direct
OL,18,Fpeople out of the building.
