OL,3,CBangkok fire death toll rises to 32 as
OL,4,Ctwo die in hospital
OL,6,FSurvivors and family members of
OL,7,Fvictims were seeking compensation to
OL,8,Fpay for funerals.
OL,10,FThey will initially receive 10,000
OL,11,Fbaht (approximately #221), a lawyer
OL,12,Frepresenting the bar owners told local
OL,13,Fmedia.
